ComicInfo.Title: Little Sister, Don't You (a.k.a Dark Streets, Snap City) Part Four!
ComicInfo.Summary: LaLa Wah Wah has It Girl right where she wants her: under her boot! The truth about who this mysterious inter-dimensional villain really is comes to light, and the Atomics will have to rally everything they have to stop her. Featuring art from the Eisner-winning team behind Battlepug!
